object.customQuery:
select distinct a.systemid,
a.parentid,
a.cmmcontainer,
a.id,
a.addrtypecd,
a.addr1,
a.addr2,
a.addr3,
a.addr4,
a.city,
a.stateprovcd,
a.postalcode,
a.county,
ad.uw_dashboard_address_details_row_id as tgt_row_id,
ad.uw_dashboard_address_details_md5_hash_value as tgt_md5_hash_value,
ad.uw_dashboard_address_details_row_effective_end_datetime as tgt_row_effective_end_date
from dbo.addr_stg a
left outer join (
	select
		uw_dashboard_address_details_row_id,
		uw_dashboard_address_details_md5_hash_value,
		address_system_id,
		uw_dashboard_address_details_row_effective_end_datetime,
		address_id,
		address_cmm_container,
		address_parent_id
		
	from
		dbo.uw_dashboard_address_details
	where
		uw_dashboard_address_details_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31') ad 
		on
	ad.address_system_id = a.systemid
	and ad.address_parent_id = a.parentid
	and ad.address_id = a.id
	and ad.address_cmm_container = a.cmmcontainer
WHERE a.cmmcontainer IN ('Application','Policy')
AND a.addrtypecd IN (
'InsuredMailingAddr','CoverageStreetAddr')

fields.expression:
MD5('systemid' || systemid ||			
'parentid' ||	parentid ||
'cmmcontainer' ||	cmmcontainer ||
'id' ||	id	||
'addrtypecd' ||	addrtypecd ||
'addr1'	|| addr1 ||
'addr2' || addr2 ||
'addr3'	|| addr3 ||
'addr4' || addr4 ||
'city' || city ||
'stateprovcd' || stateprovcd ||
'postalcode' ||	postalcode ||
'county' ||	county 
)
